column2: SELECT E.SystemStudentID AS StudentID, E.GradeLevel AS EnrollmentGrade, E.SchoolYear4Digit AS SchoolYear4Digit, T.TestPeriod AS Period, T.TestSubjectGroup AS AssessmentSubject, # AS MetricSource, T.TestType AS MetricName, CONVERT (int, T.TestScore) AS Score, # AS IsMostRecent FROM Enrollment AS E INNER JOIN TestScores as T ON E.SystemStudentID = T.SystemStudentID WHERE E.EnrollmentStatus = # AND E.IsActiveEnrollment = #;
